## State Machine

States are checked **in order**. The first matching condition is the current state.

```
[INITIAL] ──► [STATE-A] ──► [STATE-B] ──► [TERMINAL]
                                │
                                ▼
                           [FAILURE]
```

### Detection Rules (evaluated in order)

1. <condition> → **[INITIAL]**
2. <condition> → **[STATE-A]**
3. <condition> → **[STATE-B]**
4. <condition> → **[TERMINAL]**
5. <condition> → **[FAILURE]**

